Requirements
	1.Have a homepage that shows recent top rated movies and recently released movies.
	2. Have an image and description for each movie.
	3. Allow for login, with moderator, admin, and user accounts.
	4. Make rating system based on user average(hearts).
	5. Allow for comment management between users and moderators.
	6. Allow users to comment on or leave reviews on movie pages.
	7. Allow user to sort movies by different parameters.
	8. Make a request queue.
	9. Allow user to submit a request to add a movie to the repository.
	10. Display requested movies in pages for admins to accept or deny both with comments.
